
## .gitignore

```gitignore
# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
build/
dist/
.venv/
venv/
.env/

# --- Jupyter ---
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- AllenSDK / Neuropixels downloads & caches ---
# Notebooks commonly use ./allendata (and sometimes ./converted) as the cache root.
allendata/
converted/
data/

# Generated AllenSDK tracking file (often inside cache dirs, but ignore globally too)
manifest.json

# Large downloaded data artifacts (usually inside cache dirs, but keep these out of git regardless)
*.nwb
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.tif
*.tiff

# OS/editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db.DS_Store
.DS_Store
